aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1684956a35571e761d53f942ef778957c5d99983","tid":378420,"uid":115904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"試過同同事兩個人食飯，平時都多偈傾既，以為多數坐對面可以傾下偈，點知我坐低之後，佢就好快咁坐左響我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n男仔真係會諗坐對面同坐隔離係有唔同？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a575be57818ca0dad7d1f237a912845ef042b0e0","tid":378420,"uid":31920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"卡位 對面<br />\n方枱 隔離"},{"pid":"aaf580ed499c6b7705e7d25bf61cb36ab0b2b1dc","tid":378420,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"坐大脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7922c0abad931a438ffe27e73741cc3fcc190090","tid":378420,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:01:38.000Z","msg":"隔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜佢唔會咁做"},{"pid":"ce7210f3d44a2543f8ab1068cb4338b74590839f","tid":378420,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39074b951dea6bbcc2cc483efd82b6057910591f","tid":378420,"uid":6583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"4人位呢<br />\n對面吉左咪好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前同ex玩野 卡位坐佢隔離 佢即刻叫佢死返過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c6e3bb443e107d12b8354008fc9c89c656506b","tid":378420,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4人位呢<br />\n對面吉左咪好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b